<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">The United States</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">the European Union</ENAMEX> will start lifting economic sanctions against <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Yugoslavia</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">today</ENAMEX> .
